      "text": [
        "473 - وَ سَأَلَهُ اَلْفَضْلُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اَلْمَلِكِ: هَلْ يُصَلَّى عَلَى اَلْمَيِّتِ فِي اَلْمَسْجِدِ قَالَ «نَعَمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.473 - Al-Fadl ibn Abd al-Malik asked Imam (as): \"Is it permissible to perform the funeral prayer for the deceased in the mosque?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes”."
        ]
      }
    }
